<div class="aside-image-wrapper">
<figure class="aside-image"><a href="https://thefederalist.com/2019/02/27/left-willing-condemn-protecting-gay-people-lynchings-trump/" title="Left Willing To Condemn Protecting Gay People From Lynchings If Trump Does It"><img src="https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/themes/attitude-child/images/pixel.gif" data-lazy-src="https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528-998x666.jpg" width="998" height="666" class="attachment-aside-post size-aside-post wp-post-image" alt="Left Willing To Condemn Protecting Gay People From Lynchings If Trump Does It" title="Left Willing To Condemn Protecting Gay People From Lynchings If Trump Does It" srcset="https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528-998x666.jpg 998w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528-300x200.jpg 300w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528-405x270.jpg 405w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528-200x133.jpg 200w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 998px) 100vw, 998px"><noscript><img width="998" height="666" src="https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528-998x666.jpg" class="attachment-aside-post size-aside-post wp-post-image" alt="Left Willing To Condemn Protecting Gay People From Lynchings If Trump Does It" title="Left Willing To Condemn Protecting Gay People From Lynchings If Trump Does It" srcset="https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528-998x666.jpg 998w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528-300x200.jpg 300w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528-405x270.jpg 405w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528-200x133.jpg 200w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/shutterstock_110663528.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 998px) 100vw, 998px" /></noscript></a></figure> </div>
